        <p>The rear of the VENUE is equally impressive, anchored by the stunning <span class="font-weight-700">Rear horizon LED tail lamp. </span>This connected light bar design provides a wide, stable visual impression. The <span class="font-weight-700">Aerodynamic spoiler with LED high mounted stop lamp </span>and the<span class="font-weight-700"> Signature C-pillar garnish</span> add a touch of sporty elegance. The commitment to detail is further evident in the subtle <span class="font-weight-700">In-glass VENUE emblem, </span>a small flourish that speaks volumes about the meticulous attention given to every element of the car’s design. From any angle, the all-new Hyundai VENUE successfully projects a sense of rugged capability merged with urban sophistication.</p>
